    {"type":"text","id":"llm_q_t","x":100,"y":2335,"width":460,"height":230,"text":"שאלון (questionnaire.ts)\n\nקוד:\n· matchAnswer() — מספר/value/substring\n· FSM 10 שלבים (9 = confirmation, 10 = done)\n· calc API call\n· routeToQuoted/Factory\n\nLLM (shipped v3.1):\n· spec-extractor — fallback ל-matchAnswer null\n  'דחוף'→s1, 'עם ידיות'→true\n· step 9 confirmation — טקסט חופשי\n  → extract: quantity, size, handles, colors, notes\n· max 2 סיבובי שינוי → factory","originalText":"שאלון (questionnaire.ts)\n\nקוד:\n· matchAnswer() — מספר/value/substring\n· FSM 10 שלבים (9 = confirmation, 10 = done)\n· calc API call\n· routeToQuoted/Factory\n\nLLM (shipped v3.1):\n· spec-extractor — fallback ל-matchAnswer null\n  'דחוף'→s1, 'עם ידיות'→true\n· step 9 confirmation — טקסט חופשי\n  → extract: quantity, size, handles, colors, notes\n· max 2 סיבובי שינוי → factory","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#1e3a5f","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":17012,"version":1,"versionNonce":17013,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":"llm_q","lineHeight":1.4},

